entries.title: Rwanda accused of 'act of war' as DRC fighter jet is hit mid-air
entries.description: The Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) on Tuesday denounced Rwanda's accusation that a Congolese fighter jet violated Rwandan airspace, alleging the aircraft was attacked by Rwandan forces in a "deliberate act of aggression that amounts to an act of war."

entries.title: Zambian student who died fighting for Russia in Ukraine laid to rest
entries.description: The Zambian student who died in battle in Ukraine was buried Wednesday in a private ceremony in his home country, a family spokesman told CNN.
